WEBVTT

00:02.603 --> 00:04.205
Previously on Empire...
I'm not giving up
on my group, Ma.

00:04.238 --> 00:06.207
If I don't find a girl
in a week, I'll drop it.

00:06.240 --> 00:08.976
Gutter Life Records--
it's a defunct label,

00:09.009 --> 00:10.044
but they got that raw sound

00:10.078 --> 00:11.712
that I've been looking for.

00:11.745 --> 00:14.182
You got something, and it
don't come around every day.

00:14.215 --> 00:15.483
Let me help you
do something with it.

00:15.516 --> 00:16.850
MAN:
Come on, Freda!

00:16.884 --> 00:18.652
You need a god to produce you.

00:18.686 --> 00:20.521
You need me to produce.

00:20.554 --> 00:21.989
JAMAL: I feel like
you're the new Warhol.

00:22.022 --> 00:23.591
God, you are gorgeous.

00:24.725 --> 00:26.360
(grunts)

00:27.528 --> 00:29.697
Lucious-- he wants
your music, Cookie.

00:29.730 --> 00:30.698
He wants everything.

00:30.731 --> 00:31.899
God's been speaking to me.

00:31.932 --> 00:34.168
He wants me to keep
seeking Empire.

00:34.202 --> 00:36.036
What'd you do
to your Uncle Vernon?

00:36.070 --> 00:37.238
Stop it! Stop it!

00:37.271 --> 00:38.239
(grunts, gasps)

00:39.107 --> 00:40.508
You saved my life.

00:40.541 --> 00:42.343
Welcome back
to the Empire.

00:42.376 --> 00:43.811
(screams)

00:45.045 --> 00:46.380
From the streets of Philadelphia

00:46.414 --> 00:48.216
to the top
of the Billboard charts

00:48.249 --> 00:50.384
to the balcony
of the New York Stock Exchange,

00:50.418 --> 00:52.753
to a prison cell in Brooklyn,

00:52.786 --> 00:55.223
Lucious Lyon has emerged
a free man.

00:55.256 --> 00:57.391
(cheering)
After a four-month ordeal,

00:57.425 --> 00:59.393
all charges against him
have been dropped,

00:59.427 --> 01:02.430
and Judge Erskine Robbins has
granted the motion to dismiss.

01:02.463 --> 01:04.098
Now, that's how
you close a case.

01:04.132 --> 01:07.701
Yeah, they ain't really
calling it a suicide?

01:07.735 --> 01:09.203
Yeah, the Feds
are embarrassed.

01:09.237 --> 01:12.206
Had no case without him.
Damn sure don't want nobody

01:12.240 --> 01:14.775
to know the dead body popped up
in the prosecutor's car.

01:14.808 --> 01:16.310
(laughing)
So I heard.

01:16.344 --> 01:18.078
Good to see you.

01:24.084 --> 01:25.919
(sighs)
LUCIOUS:
Andre!

01:26.954 --> 01:29.323
Welcome back to
the Empire, son.

01:29.357 --> 01:30.958
Congratulations, Pop.

01:30.991 --> 01:32.293
You beat the rap.

01:32.326 --> 01:34.128
Yeah. Thanks to you.

01:34.162 --> 01:38.065
And that prosecutor-- she,
uh... took a leave of absence.

01:38.098 --> 01:39.800
Let's not talk
about that here, Pop.

01:39.833 --> 01:42.069
Okay. Business it is.

01:42.102 --> 01:45.239
Oh, by the way, I signed
a new artist to your label,

01:45.273 --> 01:46.940
Gutter Life--
her name's Freda Gatz.

01:46.974 --> 01:48.676
You're gonna meet her
later on.

01:48.709 --> 01:50.944
Andre, nice to see you
without a shovel.

01:50.978 --> 01:52.913
We got a slew
of reporters outside.

01:52.946 --> 01:55.749
They ain't gonna go away until
they get a statement from you.

01:55.783 --> 01:56.917
I'm not saying nothing to them

01:56.950 --> 01:58.419
so they can twist
my words around.

01:58.452 --> 02:00.288
No, you really should make
some sort of statement, Pop.

02:00.321 --> 02:01.255
THIRSTY:
Yeah.

02:01.289 --> 02:02.623
To the Empire!

02:02.656 --> 02:04.358
I mean, that's your thing,
right?

02:04.392 --> 02:05.826
Yeah. Y'all want me
to say something?

02:05.859 --> 02:07.828
THIRSTY:
Yeah.

02:07.861 --> 02:09.697
Let me see your phone.

02:13.967 --> 02:15.936
COOKIE:
Throw your hair back. Uh-huh.

02:15.969 --> 02:18.472
The angle is here, honey.
Up, up.

02:18.506 --> 02:20.608
Work the camera, honey.

02:20.641 --> 02:21.809
Yes, girl! Work!

02:21.842 --> 02:25.112
We need some more oil
on her legs, honey.

02:25.145 --> 02:26.614
* 'Cause now I'm like,
ooh, ooh *

02:26.647 --> 02:28.349
* See me up
in the club, like... *

02:28.382 --> 02:29.850
Yeah, I think
we got it, T. Cool?

02:29.883 --> 02:31.785
Okay. Thanks.
Mm-hmm.

02:31.819 --> 02:33.621
Oh, thank you.

02:33.654 --> 02:34.655
(smacks lips)

02:34.688 --> 02:37.157
(sighs)
What's up?

02:37.191 --> 02:39.660
Porsha set up this dumb phone
with these stupid-ass alerts,

02:39.693 --> 02:41.161
and I can't figure it out.

02:41.195 --> 02:43.464
Can you fix it?
Where is she, anyways?

02:43.497 --> 02:45.499
I fired her
'cause she got me arrested.

02:45.533 --> 02:46.734
Now, fix my phone.

02:46.767 --> 02:47.968
(phone beeping)

02:48.001 --> 02:49.803
Uh, it's Lucious.

02:49.837 --> 02:51.205
What?

02:51.239 --> 02:52.340
Hey, Ma, I want you
to meet somebody.

02:52.373 --> 02:55.042
Boy, get over here and see
what your father posted.

02:57.578 --> 03:00.481
LUCIOUS (over video):
The truth is, I'm innocent.

03:00.514 --> 03:03.484
I was being targeted-- nobody
ever had a case against me.

03:03.517 --> 03:06.320
And all those people that think
they got a problem with me,

03:06.354 --> 03:07.488
y'all can kiss my ass.

03:07.521 --> 03:09.657
Your father's
a heartless bastard.

03:09.690 --> 03:11.825
Vernon's body ain't even...
Mom.

03:11.859 --> 03:14.662
Tiana, I want you to meet
my new lead singer Laura.

03:14.695 --> 03:16.864
Laura, meet Tiana.
Oh, my gosh, I'm a big fan.

03:16.897 --> 03:18.466
Thank you.

03:21.068 --> 03:22.770
Tiana, uh, can you show Laura

03:22.803 --> 03:24.372
to the studio? I'll be
in there in a minute.

03:24.405 --> 03:26.340
Yeah.
Thank you, babe.

03:26.374 --> 03:27.475
Mm-hmm.

03:29.910 --> 03:31.412
Are you two...?

03:31.445 --> 03:33.180
Uh, no. Not anymore.

03:33.213 --> 03:35.015
He's like that with
all the girls.

03:35.048 --> 03:38.218
But he was just telling me and
Cookie that you can really blow.

03:38.252 --> 03:40.688
What?
He thinks you got
a million-dollar voice.

03:40.721 --> 03:42.623
You know,
I can't wait to see

03:42.656 --> 03:44.758
what he's gonna do
with you all.

03:44.792 --> 03:48.161
You really think
Vernon offed himself?

03:53.066 --> 03:54.802
Look, where we from,

03:54.835 --> 03:56.870
if snitches
don't kill themselves,

03:56.904 --> 03:58.706
somebody else will.

03:58.739 --> 04:02.543
Look, I ain't
studying Lucious.

04:02.576 --> 04:04.878
But if we want
this craziness to stop,

04:04.912 --> 04:06.747
it's got to start with us.

04:06.780 --> 04:08.949
Okay? Now, we got
a good thing, son,

04:08.982 --> 04:10.718
a good thing-- look at this.

04:10.751 --> 04:12.152
So I need you to focus.

04:12.185 --> 04:14.288
And you got this video
coming out with Jamal.

04:14.322 --> 04:17.391
I need you to get back in the
studio and make some more tracks

04:17.425 --> 04:20.494
so you can ride this publicity
that you're gonna get, okay?

04:20.528 --> 04:22.896
All right, handsome?

04:22.930 --> 04:25.132
Why you not smiling?

04:25.165 --> 04:27.835
Fix my phone. Porsha put
some damn alerts on there--

04:27.868 --> 04:30.070
I can't get it off.

04:30.103 --> 04:32.306
* Get it, girl,
get, get, get, get it *

04:32.340 --> 04:33.841
* Get it, girl...

04:33.874 --> 04:35.008
Welcome home.

04:35.042 --> 04:36.410
(applause, whooping)

04:36.444 --> 04:37.845
Gutter Life!

04:37.878 --> 04:39.413
OTHERS:
Gutter Life!

04:39.447 --> 04:42.115
* Get it, girl,
get, get, get, get it *

04:42.149 --> 04:44.151
* Get it, girl, get it, girl

04:44.184 --> 04:46.620
* Get it, girl,
get, get, get, get it *

04:46.654 --> 04:48.589
* Bend it over, baby,
let me see you act up *

04:48.622 --> 04:52.360
* Yeah, I can make the money fly
like NASA, I can *

04:52.393 --> 04:53.961
* I'm electric, you can
catch me in that Tesla *

04:53.994 --> 04:56.330
* Michael Phelps cool, but I
could stroke you way better... *

04:56.364 --> 04:57.598
Ladies and gentlemen,

04:57.631 --> 05:01.435
today is a historic day
for Gutter Life and you artists,

05:01.469 --> 05:04.338
'cause on this day you meet
your new king

05:04.372 --> 05:08.476
and president, my son,
Mr. Andre Lyon!

05:08.509 --> 05:10.878
(cheering)

05:13.481 --> 05:15.148
Congratulations, boss.

05:15.182 --> 05:16.850
Ready to get Gutter with us?

05:16.884 --> 05:19.653
* Who dem wild boys,
that dude payin' *

05:19.687 --> 05:20.654
* Who dat?

05:20.688 --> 05:22.155
* You know what it is

05:22.189 --> 05:23.357
* Who dem wild boys?

05:23.391 --> 05:25.058
* They do it real clean

05:25.092 --> 05:27.795
* Who dat?
That's the way we live *

05:27.828 --> 05:29.497
* Who dem wild boys?

05:29.530 --> 05:31.665
* Who da wild boys?

05:31.699 --> 05:33.033
* Who dat?
* Who dem wild boys?

05:33.066 --> 05:34.868
* Who da wild boys?

05:34.902 --> 05:37.304
* Who da wild boys... eh?

05:37.337 --> 05:38.972
* Who da wild boys, eh?

05:39.006 --> 05:41.274
* Step in the room,
they say damn... *

05:50.117 --> 05:52.753
* I was born to love... you

05:52.786 --> 05:54.988
* And nobody else will do

05:55.022 --> 05:59.092
* I would rather die
than live without you *

05:59.126 --> 06:01.429
* And everybody know it, too

06:01.462 --> 06:04.598
* Don't know why we go to war

06:04.632 --> 06:07.668
* But the one thing
that's for sure *

06:07.701 --> 06:12.005
* I was born to love you

06:12.039 --> 06:13.006
* I know I'm...

06:13.040 --> 06:14.775
No, no, no, no. When you get

06:14.808 --> 06:16.744
to that second
"I was born to love you,"

06:16.777 --> 06:18.946
it's the moment of creation,
it's the Big Bang.

06:18.979 --> 06:21.114
You've got to feel
the whole universe.

06:21.148 --> 06:22.416
All right.

06:22.450 --> 06:23.717
Ne-Yo, what you think?

06:25.318 --> 06:27.254
Be honest with him, man.

06:27.287 --> 06:28.556
Don't hold back.

06:28.589 --> 06:29.790
He needs it.

06:29.823 --> 06:32.092
(clears throat)

06:32.125 --> 06:35.062
It's definitely a record where
the passion needs to be epic.

06:35.095 --> 06:37.731
Personal opinion--
not bad.

06:37.765 --> 06:39.633
Thank you. Means a lot
coming from you.

06:39.667 --> 06:41.368
Indeed.

06:41.401 --> 06:42.936
Honest enough?

06:42.970 --> 06:44.738
You know what,
if y'all thinking like that,

06:44.772 --> 06:46.807
then why don't y'all just do
a little collaboration.

06:46.840 --> 06:49.477
I mean, lay down a couple
tracks, see what happens.

06:49.510 --> 06:52.813
You real smart, but you
behind the game, old man.

06:52.846 --> 06:54.281
We already been talking.
It's gonna happen.

06:54.314 --> 06:55.749
Yeah, I got a
little free time.

06:55.783 --> 06:57.451
I figured I'd come
out on the road

06:57.485 --> 07:00.588
for a couple dates, you know,
debut some of the new stuff.

07:00.621 --> 07:02.422
See, now that's a move
your mama can't make.

07:02.456 --> 07:03.957
That's that thing
that pushes you up

07:03.991 --> 07:05.392
to that whole other level.

07:05.425 --> 07:06.760
MICHAEL:
Hey.

07:06.794 --> 07:09.663
Sorry, the gallery opening's
in 30, so we got to...

07:09.697 --> 07:11.231
Michael, Ne-Yo.

07:11.264 --> 07:12.399
How you doing, brother?
Wow!

07:12.432 --> 07:13.901
Man, I'm a huge fan.
I've been to,

07:13.934 --> 07:15.636
like, 20 of your concerts
or something.

07:15.669 --> 07:17.905
Ah, that's love.
Appreciate it, bro.
Yeah.

07:17.938 --> 07:19.807
Ne-Yo's gonna come out
on a few dates of my tour.

07:19.840 --> 07:21.642
Wait, so he...
you're coming with us?

07:21.675 --> 07:22.576
Yes, sir.

07:22.610 --> 07:23.744
I love that!

07:23.777 --> 07:25.112
MICHAEL:
Wow.

07:27.848 --> 07:29.583
Michael, why don't you
meet me in my office?

07:29.617 --> 07:30.818
I'm gonna just
wrap it up.

07:30.851 --> 07:32.953
Yeah. Great to meet you, Ne-Yo.

07:32.986 --> 07:34.622
Nice to meet you, bro.

07:37.625 --> 07:39.860
That's a mistake.

07:39.893 --> 07:42.996
First rule of the road is
you don't bring your girlfriend.

07:43.030 --> 07:44.565
I mean, boyfriend.

07:45.799 --> 07:47.300
Why is that?

07:47.334 --> 07:50.704
'Cause you need to be...
in seduction mode on that stage.

07:50.738 --> 07:52.005
No distractions.

07:52.039 --> 07:53.707
Dad, I kind of feel like
you're the last person

07:53.741 --> 07:54.708
to give me relationship advice.

07:54.742 --> 07:56.043
(chuckles)

07:56.076 --> 07:57.878
Ask your man.

07:57.911 --> 07:59.880
(sighs) Touring gets lonely.

07:59.913 --> 08:01.682
You know that, L.
Bingo.

08:01.715 --> 08:03.717
Now, I mean, don't get me wrong,
there's a multitude

08:03.751 --> 08:05.285
of temporary
companionship if you,

08:05.318 --> 08:06.820
you know, if you
'bout that life.

08:06.854 --> 08:08.488
I ain't 'bout that life.

08:08.522 --> 08:10.323
But after a while,
you do start, you know,

08:10.357 --> 08:12.660
craving something real, and
if he already got the real...

08:12.693 --> 08:14.194
I say, why not.

08:14.227 --> 08:15.462
To hell with what he's saying.

08:15.495 --> 08:17.364
You need to be focused.

08:17.397 --> 08:19.166
Everything you want
is on the line.

08:19.199 --> 08:20.901
Can't let nothing get
in the way of your moment.

08:20.934 --> 08:22.903
I'll be back.

08:26.106 --> 08:28.576
MAN:
Tough first day back, huh?

08:28.609 --> 08:31.478
ANDRE: My father's reviving an
old label, Gutter Life Records,

08:31.511 --> 08:34.181
(chuckles): which is
exactly what it sounds like.

08:34.214 --> 08:37.050
He appointed me
president.

08:37.084 --> 08:38.485
He's testing you.

08:38.518 --> 08:41.922
Just like he did
with the music therapist.

08:41.955 --> 08:43.256
Michelle.

08:43.290 --> 08:45.358
And she led you to the Lord.

08:45.392 --> 08:47.494
There's a purpose
to all of it.

08:47.527 --> 08:49.863
I need to protect
my family.

08:51.198 --> 08:53.333
I think it's time, I do.

08:53.366 --> 08:57.838
We take baptism at my church
very seriously, Andre.

08:57.871 --> 08:59.940
It requires action...

08:59.973 --> 09:01.508
and devotion.
I'm committed, Reverend.

09:01.541 --> 09:04.011
You tell me what I need to do,
and I'll do it.

09:04.044 --> 09:07.247
First, clear your conscience.

09:07.280 --> 09:10.383
Go to your loved ones, confess
all your sins against them.

09:10.417 --> 09:12.352
Then...

09:12.385 --> 09:13.854
invite them to your baptism.

09:13.887 --> 09:15.689
Confess to my family?

09:15.723 --> 09:18.191
(laughs)

09:18.225 --> 09:22.262
Your house ain't clean
if your closets are dirty.

09:22.295 --> 09:24.531
Reverend, my family
doesn't go to a church

09:24.564 --> 09:26.566
unless somebody's in a casket.

09:26.600 --> 09:29.102
Hmm.

09:29.136 --> 09:31.905
Maybe he wants you
to be his shepherd.

09:31.939 --> 09:35.643
Maybe God wants you
to lead them here.

09:37.110 --> 09:39.112
Maybe.

09:42.415 --> 09:44.117
WOMAN:
Great shoot, T.

09:44.151 --> 09:46.486
You need a lift?
No, thank you. I got
a car on the way.

09:46.519 --> 09:48.388
Thanks, though.
All right. Bye.

09:48.421 --> 09:50.223
Bye.

09:50.257 --> 09:52.559
WOMAN: Oh, snap!
Look, it's Tiana!

09:52.592 --> 09:53.994
Hey, yo, could we get
a flick with you?

09:54.027 --> 09:54.962
Sure.

10:01.268 --> 10:03.336
(camera clicks)

10:03.370 --> 10:04.838
Ah...

10:04.872 --> 10:06.439
one more, one more.

10:07.641 --> 10:09.843
Get off of me!

10:09.877 --> 10:11.111
Stop!

10:11.144 --> 10:12.312
I want that bag, bitch.

10:12.345 --> 10:14.581
Oh, my God!

10:14.614 --> 10:16.316
Keep it movin'!

10:16.349 --> 10:17.417
Help!

10:17.450 --> 10:19.853
Give me my bag!

10:26.193 --> 10:27.260
Yo, what happened?
She got jacked

10:27.294 --> 10:28.128
right outside our front door.
By who?

10:28.161 --> 10:29.997
Two ugly-ass bitches.

10:30.030 --> 10:31.098
You good?
CHICKEN: Hey, y'all,
check this out.

10:31.131 --> 10:32.933
Look what I found on YouTube.

10:32.966 --> 10:33.967
What?

10:34.001 --> 10:36.503
Oh! Oh... look at this!

10:36.536 --> 10:38.839
(woman laughing)
HAKEEM:
Hey, what are they wearing?

10:38.872 --> 10:40.273
WOMAN:
We in that 420, honey.

10:40.307 --> 10:42.976
MAN: Welcome to my kingdom,
Lyon Dynasty.

10:43.010 --> 10:45.713
You wanna chillax here,
you gon' pay tax here.

10:45.746 --> 10:47.047
(laughter over video)

10:47.080 --> 10:48.515
What, is this dude trying
to get signed or something?

10:48.548 --> 10:50.317
No.
MAN: Won't be
no collection agency

10:50.350 --> 10:52.319
sending you
past-due notices, either.

10:52.352 --> 10:53.721
It'll me kicking down your door.

10:53.754 --> 10:54.888
(man continues in Spanish)

10:54.922 --> 10:57.290
Damn. We've been marked.

10:57.324 --> 10:59.960
They're gonna try to
extort money from us.

10:59.993 --> 11:01.895
Has this happened before?
No.

11:01.929 --> 11:03.563
And it's not gonna start.

11:03.596 --> 11:05.833
I'm-a take care of this,
trust and believe that.

11:08.101 --> 11:10.570
* Be alone, oh, oh

11:10.603 --> 11:15.142
* Whoo, I can't feel my face
when I'm with you *

11:15.175 --> 11:17.144
* But I love it...

11:17.177 --> 11:19.679
Yeah, go back.
Those ones, too.

11:19.713 --> 11:22.883
Just, uh... see that?

11:22.916 --> 11:25.485
(exhales)

11:25.518 --> 11:27.487
This is what
I live for.

11:27.520 --> 11:29.823
Everyday people
taking photos of my art

11:29.857 --> 11:31.324
and posting their own
interpretations of it.

11:31.358 --> 11:33.260
You know, when
your music video

11:33.293 --> 11:34.828
goes viral-- which it will--

11:34.862 --> 11:37.064
the price of the original
is gonna just skyrocket.

11:37.097 --> 11:38.565
I want the original.

11:38.598 --> 11:41.001
You already got the original.

11:41.034 --> 11:42.269
MICHAEL:
I do.

11:42.302 --> 11:43.737
Look at you two.

11:43.771 --> 11:46.539
You guys
are hot together.
(chuckles)

11:46.573 --> 11:49.509
Look, I hope you let me use
some of this art for my tour.

11:49.542 --> 11:51.711
That calls for another bottle.

11:51.745 --> 11:53.947
Hey, would you mind?

11:53.981 --> 11:55.783
What about you-- you going
on the road with him or what?

11:55.816 --> 11:59.386
Uh, my dad's already trying
to get into my head and say

11:59.419 --> 12:02.289
don't bring the relationship
on the road, so we'll see.

12:02.322 --> 12:04.524
Well, I mean, it's
Lucious, so...

12:04.557 --> 12:06.426
Personally,
I'm with Lucious on this one.

12:06.459 --> 12:09.930
Relationships are
the death of creativity.

12:09.963 --> 12:11.564
Why would you say that?

12:11.598 --> 12:13.700
You mean to tell me
you've never been in love?

12:13.733 --> 12:15.735
Every day.

12:15.769 --> 12:17.470
